markets.description:
This market will resolve according to the team that wins the 2025 MLB American League (ie advance to the 2025 MLB World Series). 

If at any point it becomes impossible for this team to win the American League based on the rules of the MLB (e.g., they are eliminated from the playoffs), this market will immediately resolve to “No”.

If the 2025  MLB season is permanently canceled or has not been completed by February 28, 2026, 11:59 PM this market will resolve to “Other”.

events.description:
This market will resolve according to the team that wins the 2025 MLB American League (ie advance to the 2025 MLB World Series). Otherwise, this market will resolve to “No”.

If at any point it becomes impossible for this team to win the American League based on the rules of the MLB (e.g., they are eliminated from the playoffs), this market will immediately resolve to “No”.

If the 2025  MLB season is permanently canceled or has not been completed by February 28, 2026, 11:59 PM this market will resolve to “Other”.
